{"tid":1063690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聯合國准參加人權會議　外交部副部長：廣泛認同中國人權事業成就","createTime":"2019-03-16T03:20:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-16T03:36:59.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dc1c9e3560577e1911b7a2ecf300f5a67ab8b79e","tid":1063690,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T03:20:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190316/s00004/29eed7609fcf7c017431d08c9ea1d610.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190316%2Fs00004%2F29eed7609fcf7c017431d08c9ea1d610.jpg&h=3d1451cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聯合國人權理事會核可中國參加第三輪國別人權審議報告。中國代表團團長、外交部副部長樂玉成表示，整個進程是對中國人權事業成就、人權發展道路和人權保障決心的廣泛認同。<br />\n<br />\n樂玉成又說，中國接受各方在審議中提及的絕大多數建議的原則立場，認為符合中國國情及有利於中國人權事業發展。<br />\n<br />\n樂玉成另駁斥部分西方國家和非政府組織代表指摘，強調堅決反對以人權為藉口干涉中國內政、損害中國主權和領土完整。"},{"pid":"d7b388c7bae29c3fd1ccfcc3b6b9cbbe1405cf16","tid":1063690,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T03:20:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8/article/20190316/s00004/1552700533097/%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E5%9C%8B%E6%A0%B8%E5%8F%AF%E5%8F%83%E5%8A%A0%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0-%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8%E5%89%AF%E9%83%A8%E9%95%B7-%E5%BB%A3%E6%B3%9B%E8%AA%8D%E5%90%8C%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E4%BA%8B%E6%A5%AD%E6%88%90%E5%B0%B1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25B2%25B8%2Farticle%2F20190316%2Fs00004%2F1552700533097%2F%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2590%2588%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25A0%25B8%25E5%258F%25AF%25E5%258F%2583%25E5%258A%25A0%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25AD%25B0-%25E5%25A4%2596%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E9%2583%25A8%25E5%2589%25AF%25E9%2583%25A8%25E9%2595%25B7-%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E6%25B3%259B%25E8%25AA%258D%25E5%2590%258C%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%25E4%25BA%258B%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%25B0%2